{"word":"H5132 - נוּץ - nûwts - noots - Flee away","slug":"H5132","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">נוּץ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>nûwts"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>noots"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Flee away"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E0;&#x05D5;&#x05BC;&#x05E5; - nu&#x0302;ts</b> - <i>noots</i><p/>A primitive root; properly to <i>flash</i>; hence, to <i>blossom</i> (from the brilliancy of color); also, to <i>fly</i> away (from the quickness of motion): - flee away, bud (forth)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H5213\">H5213</a>, <a href=\"#/H5322\">H5322</a>, <a href=\"#/H5328\">H5328</a>, <a href=\"#/H5339\">H5339</a>, <a href=\"#/H5340\">H5340</a>"}]}